ttp_template:
<group name="cts_last_change_cts_status_enforcement_ep_policy">
SGT/SGPN Enforcement: {{ENFORCEMENT | ORPHRASE}}
Endpoint Policy Attribute: {{EP_POLICY | ORPHRASE}} 
Last Policy Download Status: {{LAST_POLICY_STATUS | ORPHRASE}}
Interface: {{INTERFACE | ORPHRASE}}
Status: {{CTS_STATUS | ORPHRASE}}
Last Status Change: {{CTS_LAST_CHANGE | ORPHRASE}}
</group>

textfsm_template:
Value CTS_STATUS (UP|DOWN)
Value CTS_LAST_CHANGE (\S+)
Value ENFORCEMENT (\S+)
Value EP_POLICY (\S+)
Value SGACL_POLICY (\S+)
Value LAST_POLICY_STATUS (\S+)
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value IF_STATUS (UP|DOWN)
Value IF_LAST_CHANGE (\S+)

Start
  ^CTS:\s*$$
  ^Status:\s+${CTS_STATUS}\s*$$
  ^Last\sStatus\sChange:\s+${CTS_LAST_CHANGE}\s*$$
  ^SGT\/SGPN\sEnforcement:\s+${ENFORCEMENT}\s*$$
  ^Endpoint\sPolicy\sAttribute:\s+${EP_POLICY}\s*$$
  ^SGACL\sPolicy:\s+${SGACL_POLICY}\s*$$
  ^Last\sPolicy\sDownload\sStatus:\s+${LAST_POLICY_STATUS}\s*$$
  ^$$
  ^Interface:\s+${INTERFACE}\s*$$
  ^Status:\s+${IF_STATUS}\s*$$
  ^Last\sStatus\sChange:\s+${IF_LAST_CHANGE}\s*$$ -> Record
